Chinese Airline Group Protests EU Emissions Trading System, Daily Reports

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-10T01:29:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/chinese-airline-group-protests-eu-emissions-trading-system-daily-reports.html
The  China  Air Transport Association
said the European Union’s emissions trading system will cost
them “billions of yuan” each year, China Daily reported,
citing a statement from the industry group.  The association said it will recommend “harsher
countermeasures” against flights by European carriers operated
in and out of China if the EU doesn’t change its trading system
plan, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  